ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/extras/BulletP.png?t=1724444977\" /> <strong>Market:</strong> Trade rare items, collectibles and more with other players.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/extras/BulletP.png?t=1724444977\" /> <strong>Guild System:</strong> Ascend to become the most powerful guild on the continent!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/extras/BulletP.png?t=1724444977\" /> <strong>Global Events:</strong> Minigames and some fun events may occur during certain hours, changing the pace of the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/extras/BulletP.png?t=1724444977\" /> <strong>And more:</strong> Highscores, Day and Night Cycles, Crafting, etc..<br><br>A vast world full of adventures and mysteries awaits you!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724444977","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1724444977","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/eb9ce154cb8155b2689c7f2992192dc27645f447/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724444977","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454980/eb9ce154cb8155b2689c7f2992192dc27645f447/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724444977","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detail